%F A060626 a(n) = 4*(n+1)^2 - 2 = 2*A056220(n+1). - _Bruce J. Nicholson_, Aug 31 2017
%F A060626 a(n) + a(n-1) + (n-1)^2 = (3*n + 1)^2 = A016777(n)^2. - _Ezhilarasu Velayutham_, May 23 2019
